PRESTATI DA POSTOJI.

867
01:27:33,340 --> 01:27:37,379
A OVAJ DAN ÆEMO PAMTITI VEKOVIMA...

868
01:27:38,740 --> 01:27:41,459
...KAO DAN NAJVEÆE POBEDE ISLAMA.

869
01:28:05,460 --> 01:28:06,813
BRAÆO MOJA !

870
01:28:09,300 --> 01:28:11,814
