933
01:38:09,340 --> 01:38:10,898
PALI !

934
01:38:15,900 --> 01:38:17,891
VELIKI VEZIR ! MORAMO ZAŠTITITI
VELIKOG VEZIRA !

935
01:38:18,060 --> 01:38:19,778
